Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:48.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:21.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:32.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Hogback's laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His laboratory!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a glorious mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, Cindry-chan!\NThe work of a genius... is truly art!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's clearly trying to \Nturn that into a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hogback revived all of\Nthe zombies on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only possible explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:58.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil Be Gone"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're curious about\Nwhat's inside, you should go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yo ho ho"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Brook...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A severely injured old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's obviously a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you make fun of zombies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are zombies supposed to be this full of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach them just how\Ndangerous zombies can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can teach you a thing or two\Nabout how dangerous we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,600 Million Berry Jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"His Name is Moria! The Great\NShadow-Seizing Pirate's Trap!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... what were you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... We are zombies,\Nso we were kinda buried...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we were kinda rotting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right. I was rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to be funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! Not by any means!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry! Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That right? Then I have a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did a man with a long nose,\Na woman with orange hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a raccoon dog that resembles\Na reindeer pass through here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Uh, y-yeah... Yes, yes, and yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I saw them, maybe I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But our lips are sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't allowed to share information\Non that topic with outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the rule! It's the rule!\NIt's the rule! It's the rule!...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you absolutely refuse to talk, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of them passed through!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They squealed like pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're my crewmates.\NYou didn't go after them, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're your crewmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't attack them! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. S-Same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't attack them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't attack them! We didn't\Nattack them! We didn't attack them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He attacked them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hey, you don't sell friends out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You nibbled on him a bit, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all attacked them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Don't tell him that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and the other two\Napparently raced for that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad they're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they didn't know anything about Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we really need him? Forget that weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, those were some spineless zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That didn't even count as a warm-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no idea what could be\Nlurking around the next corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:08:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Starting to\Nchicken out, Swordswuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you stupid cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lump me together with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, Disoriented Moss Head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna fight, Curly Eyebrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw what you just did!\NYou're terribly strong, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please hear me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A severely injured old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've told you before, that's a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm a severely injured old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's confusing! Just pass\Nyourself off as a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you wanna discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a man I would like you to defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you could take him down!\NHe has created countless victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all of whom could be saved\Nif you defeated him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get my shadow back,\NI'll do anything I can to thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what? Are you another\Nperson who lost his shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shadow...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, you don't have a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So who the heck stole it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Moria...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man's name is Moria. \NHe is truly terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you referring to Gecko Moria?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's him. That's the Moria I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know his name well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man's bounty used to\Nsurpass even yours, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It used to? So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Gecko Moria
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is one of the Seven Warlords of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Seven Warlords?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure, Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Gecko Moria is a man\Nshrouded in mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is that man doing \Nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I don't know. But there\Nare more than a few victims
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,left to wander this forest\Nafter he stole their shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other people here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You would be wise to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Moria has had his eye on you\Never since he invited you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He invited us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:57.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Offering of Treasure to the Sea God"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who stayed must creep around\Nthe forest in fear of the zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who took to the sea must\Nspend their lives in fear of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, it hardly feels\Nlike we're even alive anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I wish that\Njust once--once is all I ask for--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could walk under the light of the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:12:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your story? Dude, that sounds killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll help ya out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about a thing, stupid!\NYou idiot, I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're way too easy to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so quick to take on\Nsomeone else's problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, geezer! Only ladies can\Nuse tears to win people over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't make my heart throb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, hey, I was searching \Nfor the shadow thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's after us, we're gonna\Nhave to kick his butt anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So wouldn't we wind up\Nhelping you on the side?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to hear you say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we're on the side, \Nit still gives us hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Best of luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick Moria's stinky butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! The other victims\Nwere listening in on us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:13:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Excuse us for not making\Nyour heart throb, Curly Eyebrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:27.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil Be Gone"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:32.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil Be Gone"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with that "yo ho ho"?!\NWas that Brook just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he wasn't a skeleton!\NHe had skin and muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus he was wearing sandals\Nand carrying a katana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:43.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they blow me off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! He was wearing\Na completely different outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infidels!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it perfectly clear to\Nkeep your noses out of my lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I didn't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Neither did I!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! I didn't see anything either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cross my heart! I swear I didn't\Nsee a zombie in the works!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what secrets\Nyou uncover. It's too late anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a couple of minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the "night raid" will begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Night raid"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We round up the unsuspecting guests\Nwho wander onto this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the night raid begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just had to rebury the zombies\Nright before the night raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't feel something\Neven if it was itchy, hot, or painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now get up, Soldier Zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you're defeated,\Nyou can rise and attack again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what makes zombies truly terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get your act together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break, zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dare you to say who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're our leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're our leader, Absalom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader! Leader! Leader! Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader! Leader! Leader! Leader!...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peeping Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erotic Leader! Erosalom! Erosalom! Eros!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Pervert! Pervert! Pervert!...\N--Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Welcome back, Perona-sama... in bulk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! Don't talk, Kumacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must you have such a deep voice\Nwhen you're so cute?! It's annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't cute, you have\Nno right to serve me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting! It's starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the night raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost midnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nin, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:19:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was having a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dreadfully wonderful, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been roughly four days\Nsince our last night raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been asleep that\Nentire time, Moria-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, we have prepared\Nfour days' worth of food for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have some impressive prey this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After toppling Enies Lobby,\Nthey've become a hot topic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Straw Hat Luffy and his gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you will find\Nuse for them, Moria-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming down pretty heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's run for the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see somethin' huge behind the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like some kinda massive mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fog has cleared up a bit, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? A flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Isn't that a sail?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still following us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as that man said, it's a sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's so large that you\Ncan't see the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thriller Bark is carrying an entire village,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making it the largest \Npirate ship in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pirate ship that \Nhauls around a village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the largest in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense. "Bark" is definitely a word\Nused to define a type of sailing ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never thought I'd see a\Nship carry an entire village...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see how the main mast\Nconnects to the back of the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is where you will find Gecko Moria.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, my Soldier Zombie Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The General Zombies will\Ntake those pirates down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times they defeat you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stand back up and renew your attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive them into a corner with\Nyour terrifying immortality!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the clock has struck midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.53,0:22:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for us to go all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't count on escaping us, foolish pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, zombies?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the land of the \Ndeceased, Thriller Bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May you have unpleasant nightmares!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a haunted mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has finally begun, Absalom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! It's time for the night raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The night raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a rampage, General Zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A night raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.60,0:23:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Feast of the Zombie Song! The Night\NRaid's Bell is the Sound of Darkness!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
